reviewText: This had a very good story, only thing was there wasn't enough cosplay scenes only the final 2 minutes we see actual cosplaying in the so called CosPlay cafe. This Hentai needs to be remade with a more PROMISING TITLE. I recommend Cosplay Sex Machine by Kitty Media, that one is a 1000 times better.(Shape Shifting Android included). Not all Hentai is excellent.

This hentai was really good. The story and the graphics were done nicely. This hentai was made in 2004, so you got to remember that the animation was done 12 years ago. For being a older hentai like I said were done really well. On a scale of 1 to 10, this is a nine.

DO.NOT.BUY.THIS.CRAP.
It's dated animation at it's worst, the story is incoherent and the animation and character designs look like the work of rejects or anime rookies. You can tell they didn't spend JACK on production and I'm embarrassed to have this bunk in my collection.

The best thing this title has going for it is the box art-that's it. The actual anime looks NOWHERE near that good. Avoid this trash.
